      build.

    * ext/mime_magic/mime_magic.c
      ext/standard/aggregation.c
      ext/standard/basic_functions.c
      ext/standard/image.c
      main/SAPI.c
      main/output.c:
      Fixed compile failures when ZLIB / PCRE are compiled as shared
      extensions in same build.

